bu Amina Elias","date":"September 11, 2010","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: Al-Aqra' ibn Habis saw the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, kissing his grandson Al-Hasan. He said, \u201cI have ten children and I do not kiss any of them.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cVerily, whoever does not show mercy will not receive mercy.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5997,\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":7561,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/10\/03\/rahmah-to-children-mercy\/","url_meta":{"origin":34105,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: The Prophet is merciful to children","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 3, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: A\u00a0bedouin\u00a0came to the Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, and he said, \u201cYou kiss the children? We do not kiss them.\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cI cannot put mercy into your heart if Allah has removed it from you.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 5998, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2317 Grade: Muttafaqun\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":25557,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/12\/06\/mercy-believers-cursed\/","url_meta":{"origin":34105,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Curses: O Allah, have mercy on believers I cursed","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 6, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cO Allah, I am only a human being. Whenever I scold, curse, or punish a Muslim man, then turn it into purification and mercy for him.\u201d Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 6361, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2601 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":389,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2011\/01\/18\/no-mercy-unless-show-mercy\/","url_meta":{"origin":34105,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Mercy: Allah is not merciful to the unmerciful","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 18, 2011","format":false,"excerpt":"Jarir ibn 'Abdillah reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \"Allah will not be merciful to those who are not merciful to people.\" Source: S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 al-Bukha\u0304ri\u0304 7376, S\u0323ah\u0323i\u0304h\u0323 Muslim 2319 Grade: Muttafaqun Alayhi\u00a0(authenticity agreed upon) according to Al-Bukhari and Muslim \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0631\u0650\u064a\u0631\u0650 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0652\u062f\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u064e\u0651\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6427,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/15\/none-paradise-except-mercy\/","url_meta":{"origin":34105,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Rahmah: None enters Paradise but by Allah&#8217;s mercy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 15, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"Aisha reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cFollow the right course, be devoted, and give glad tidings. Verily, none of you will enter Paradise by his deeds alone.\u201d They said, \u201cNot even you, O Messenger of Allah?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cNot even myself, unless\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":6580,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2012\/09\/17\/muhammad-prophet-tawbah-rahmah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34105,"position":5},"title":"Hadith on Muhammad: Prophet of repentance, Prophet of mercy","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"September 17, 2012","format":false,"excerpt":"\u201cI am Muhammad; I am Ahmad; I am the ender of Prophethood; I am the gatherer on the Day of Resurrection; I am the Prophet of repentance; and I am the Prophet of mercy.\u201d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0627 \u0645\u064f\u062d\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0651\u062f\u064c \u0648\u064e\u0623\u064e\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u062f\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u0645\u064f\u0642\u064e\u0641\u0650\u0651\u064a \u0648\u064e\u0627\u0644\u0652\u062d\u064e\u0627\u0634\u0650\u0631\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u062a\u064e\u0651\u0648\u0652\u0628\u064e\u0629\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0646\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u064f\u0651 \u0627\u0644\u0631\u064e\u0651\u062d\u0652\u0645\u064e\u0629\u0650","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/daily